    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>Student Skills</th>
      <td>Were the students adequately prepared to take the course? </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>Resources</th>
      <td>Were the textbooks, software, computers and other equipment available?</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
