      <th>Communication skills</th>
      <td>Did the students give oral presentations or write reports? Discuss strengths and weaknesses.</td>
    </tr>
    </table>
</div>



  <div class="field">
    <b>List the aspects of the course that worked</b><br>
    <%= f.text_area :comment_worked , {class: "form-control" , style:  "width:50%; height:100px;"}  %>
  </div>
  <div class="field">
    <b>What changes should be made to the course?</b><br>
